In [48]:
from wordcloud import WordCloud

Word cloud showing the distribution of countries¶

In [53]:
plt.subplots(figsize=(20,10))
wordcloud = WordCloud(
    background_color='black',
    width=1920,
    height=1080
    ).generate(" ".join(df.country))
plt.imshow(wordcloud)
plt.axis('off')
plt.savefig('country_made.png')
plt.show()
